---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Badge } from "@/components/ui/badge";
import { Card, CardContent, CardDescription, CardHeader, CardTitle } from "@/components/ui/card";

const lastUpdated = "February 7, 2026";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy" description="Privacy notice for enguerrand.dev.">
  <section class="pt-3 pb-8 sm:pt-6">
    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/85 shadow-[0_16px_42px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.06)]">
      <CardContent className="space-y-4 p-7 sm:p-9">
        <Badge variant="secondary" className="w-fit border border-border/70 bg-secondary/65">
          Legal
        </Badge>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl">Privacy Notice</h1>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground">
          This page explains what data is processed when you browse this website.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-muted-foreground">
          Last updated: {lastUpdated}
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-6">
    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">Controller</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          This website is operated by Enguerrand Allamel.
        </p>
        <p>
          Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@enguerrand.dev" class="font-medium text-primary hover:underline">hello@enguerrand.dev</a>
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">Data Processed</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>
          Minimal data is processed to deliver pages and requested content.
        </CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          Basic technical request data (for example IP address, user-agent, request time, and requested path) may be processed by the hosting platform and CDN for delivery, reliability, and abuse prevention.
        </p>
        <p>
          No user account, comment system, or on-site form submission is used on this website at this time.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">Third-Party Requests</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          Some pages can load content from third-party services when you visit them:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li>YouTube or Vimeo embeds on talks pages when a talk video is available.</li>
          <li>External websites when you click outbound links (for example GitHub, LinkedIn, or conference resources).</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These providers may receive your IP address and standard browser request metadata.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">Legal Basis (GDPR Context)</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          Where GDPR applies, processing needed to operate, secure, and deliver the website is based on legitimate interests.
        </p>
        <p>
          If non-essential analytics or tracking is introduced later, it will be based on consent where required.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">Retention and International Transfers</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          This website does not maintain visitor accounts or user profiles. Operational request logs may be retained by the hosting/CDN provider for security and reliability purposes under that provider&apos;s policies.
        </p>
        <p>
          Third-party services linked or embedded on this site may process data outside your country of residence.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">Cookies and Analytics</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          This site does not currently run first-party analytics scripts and does not set non-essential first-party tracking cookies.
        </p>
        <p>
          If analytics is added in the future, this notice will be updated and consent controls will be implemented where required (including GDPR/ePrivacy contexts).
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card className="border-border/70 bg-card/90 shadow-[0_14px_36px_hsl(var(--foreground)/0.05)]">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-2xl">GDPR Rights (EEA/UK Visitors)</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <p>
          If GDPR or equivalent laws apply to your visit, you may have rights such as access, correction, deletion, restriction, objection, and complaint to your supervisory authority.
        </p>
        <p>
          To exercise rights or ask a privacy question, email <a href="mailto:hello@enguerrand.dev" class="font-medium text-primary hover:underline">hello@enguerrand.dev</a>.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
